subject: resource/SmarTone
object: SmarTone Telecommunications Holdings Limited (Chinese: 數碼通) (0315.HK) is a wireless communications carrier with operating subsidiaries in Hong Kong and Macau. SmarTone provides voice, multimedia and broadband services through its territory-wide 4G and 3G HSPA+ networks. The carrier also uses a unique X-celerator engine to speed up Internet access.
